  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Chester\" title=\"House Chester\"><img alt=\"House Chester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/50px-House_Chester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/75px-House_Chester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/100px-House_Chester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Moribald Chester</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Chester\" title=\"House Chester\"><img alt=\"House Chester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/50px-House_Chester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/75px-House_Chester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/House_Chester.svg/100px-House_Chester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Greenshield\" title=\"Lord of Greenshield\">Lord of Greenshield</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Chester\" title=\"House Chester\">House Chester</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Greenshield\" title=\"Greenshield\">Greenshield</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Moribald Chester</b> is the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Greenshield\" title=\"Greenshield\">Greenshield</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Chester\" title=\"House Chester\">House Chester</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moribald_Chester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Moribald_Chester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>, news reaches <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> that Lord Moribald was among the slain.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-edi